---
name: Sentiment Analysis
description: >
  System prompt for sentiment classification evaluation.
  Classifies text as POSITIVE, NEGATIVE, or NEUTRAL.
  Tests sarcasm detection and mixed sentiment handling.
model:
  api: chat
  parameters:
    temperature: 0.0
    max_tokens: 16
inputs:
  text:
    type: string
    description: Text to classify by sentiment
outputs:
  label:
    type: string
    description: One of POSITIVE, NEGATIVE, NEUTRAL
---
system:
You are a sentiment analysis classifier.
Classify the sentiment of the given text as exactly one of: POSITIVE, NEGATIVE, or NEUTRAL.
Return ONLY the label, nothing else. No explanation, no punctuation, just the label.
